00:32:40,570 --> 00:32:42,120
This call from Yun Hongshen

574
00:32:42,750 --> 00:32:44,810
was from somewhere near Deyang Road.

575
00:32:49,170 --> 00:32:49,760
Madam,

576
00:32:49,790 --> 00:32:51,330
we've uncovered Myna's true identity.

577
00:32:51,330 --> 00:32:52,860
His real name is Mi Xingwei.

578
00:32:52,890 --> 00:32:53,970
He's from Changsha.

579
00:32:53,970 --> 00:32:55,100
What a coincidence,

580
00:32:55,130 --> 00:32:56,730
That nurse from the Military Hospital, Mi Lan,

581
00:32:56,730 --> 00:32:57,920
turns out to be his daughter.

582
00:32:57,920 --> 00:32:58,630
What?

583
00:32:59,050 --> 00:33:01,250
I've already sent people to watch Mi Lan's house.

584
00:33:01,250 --> 00:33:02,650
Just give it a try.

585
00:33:02,770 --> 00:33:03,830
We might get lucky.

586
00:33:03,940 --> 00:33:05,460
No. 17 Deyang Road.

587
00:33:06,470 --> 00:33:08,200
It can't be such a coincidence.

588
00:33:13,390 --> 00:33:14,550
Li Xuemin is dead.

589
00:33:14,610 --> 00:33:16,550
The ambulance arrived two minutes late.

590
00:33:16,550 --> 00:33:18,010
Those crucial two minutes

591
00:33:18,210 --> 00:33:19,320
cost Li Xueming her life.

592
00:33:19,320 --> 00:33:21,130
Then why was the ambulance late?

593
00:33:21,160 --> 00:33:22,590
The nurse accompanying the ambulance said

594
00:33:22,590 --> 00:33:24,800
they heard gunshots as they were getting close

595
00:33:24,800 --> 00:33:27,760
and thought the incident happened over there, so they went in that direction,

596
00:33:27,760 --> 00:33:29,090
which caused the delay.

597
00:33:29,740 --> 00:33:31,800
At that time, did you see two young men

598
00:33:32,120 --> 00:33:33,450
who were well-dressed?

599
00:33:33,930 --> 00:33:34,540
No.

600
00:33:34,560 --> 00:33:35,790
With so many people on the street,

601
00:33:35,790 --> 00:33:37,460
you said "no" without knowing which young men

602
00:33:37,460 --> 00:33:38,570
I was asking about?

603
00:33:40,010 --> 00:33:41,220
When the ambulance passed by,

604
00:33:41,220 --> 00:33:42,680
I glanced out of the window

605
00:33:42,930 --> 00:33:45,340
and happened to see a man in his forties walk by,

606
00:33:45,340 --> 00:33:47,000
but I didn't see two young men.

607
00:33:47,250 --> 00:33:48,980
This Mi Lan knows Yun Hongshen.

608
00:33:49,070 --> 00:33:50,700
They are likely at Mi Lan's home now.

609
00:33:50,700 --> 00:33:51,170
Hurry!

610
00:33:51,450 --> 00:33:53,030
Gather the team and head to Mi Lan's house.

611
00:33:53,030 --> 00:33:53,760
All members of Team One,

612
00:33:53,760 --> 00:33:54,320
move out!

613
00:33:55,130 --> 00:33:55,930
Mr. Wen.

614
00:33:57,180 --> 00:33:58,700
What's so urgent?

615
00:33:59,330 --> 00:34:00,460
Do you need any help?

616
00:34:00,520 --> 00:34:01,130
No need.

617
00:34:01,150 --> 00:34:01,750
Thank you.

618
00:34:58,090 --> 00:34:59,420
Why are you back so late?

619
00:34:59,950 --> 00:35:01,470
Who asked the reporter to meet?

620
00:35:01,470 --> 00:35:02,600
It was Yun Hongshen.

621
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:09,660
We've fallen into their trap.

622
00:35:09,770 --> 00:35:10,850
It seems they've already guessed

623
00:35:10,850 --> 00:35:12,380
that we have the cipher key.

624
00:35:12,710 --> 00:35:14,430
He just wanted to lure you out

625
00:35:14,460 --> 00:35:17,100
to find a way to get the cipher key from you.

626
00:35:28,340 --> 00:35:30,020
They're at No.17 Deyang Road.

627
00:35:30,570 --> 00:35:33,100
Onitetsu has repeatedly warned us not to touch Yun Hongshen.

628
00:35:33,100 --> 00:35:33,900
And our work

629
00:35:34,300 --> 00:35:36,700
has been riddled with mistakes these days.

630
00:35:41,360 --> 00:35:42,920
Are you going to listen to Onitetsu

631
00:35:42,920 --> 00:35:44,230
or to me?

632
00:35:45,690 --> 00:35:46,480
I'll listen to you.

633
00:35:46,480 --> 00:35:47,230
Remember,

634
00:35:47,780 --> 00:35:48,940
kill Yun Hongqi,

635
00:35:49,040 --> 00:35:50,300
capture Yun Hongshen,

636
00:35:50,320 --> 00:35:51,580
and find the codebook.

637
00:35:52,340 --> 00:35:53,130
Yes.

638
00:35:59,180 --> 00:35:59,850
Okay.

639
00:36:00,050 --> 00:36:00,850
I understand.

640
00:36:03,930 --> 00:36:04,720
Head nurse,

641
00:36:05,510 --> 00:36:07,330
the patients in rooms 201 to 205

642
00:36:07,350 --> 00:36:08,850
can all be discharged today.

643
00:36:08,850 --> 00:36:11,580
A new batch of wounded will be brought in tonight.

644
00:36:12,540 --> 00:36:14,870
Those on duty today are in for a tough time.

645
00:36:15,900 --> 00:36:17,300
I'll get back to work now.

646
00:36:17,570 --> 00:36:18,220
Go ahead.

647
00:36:21,540 --> 00:36:22,740
Mi Lan, what's wrong?

648
00:36:23,670 --> 00:36:24,730
-I…
-What’s wrong?

649
00:36:25,050 --> 00:36:27,340
I probably didn't sleep well last night.

650
00:36:28,280 --> 00:36:30,480
I felt dizzy when I came in this morning.

651
00:36:30,560 --> 00:36:33,470
Why am I palpitating so badly?

652
00:36:34,120 --> 00:36:35,780
You should go get checked out.

653
00:36:36,370 --> 00:36:37,180
No need.

654
00:36:37,680 --> 00:36:39,740
I'll probably be fine after resting.

655
00:36:40,370 --> 00:36:41,210
Stop working.

656
00:36:41,230 --> 00:36:42,200
Go home now.

657
00:36:43,070 --> 00:36:44,930
But the hospital is so busy today.

658
00:36:45,160 --> 00:36:46,920
Don't worry about it.

659
00:36:46,940 --> 00:36:48,530
Besides, how can you work in this condition?

660
00:36:48,530 --> 00:36:49,530
Go home now.

661
00:36:51,170 --> 00:36:51,970
Alright.

662
00:36:52,460 --> 00:36:53,480
Thank you, Head Nurse.

663
00:36:53,480 --> 00:36:54,740
Be careful on the road.

664
00:37:00,660 --> 00:37:01,500
Notify them

665
00:37:01,530 --> 00:37:03,460
to get all the hospital beds ready.

666
00:37:17,480 --> 00:37:18,270
Hurry up.

667
00:37:43,400 --> 00:37:44,720
Sir, it's here.

668
00:37:44,930 --> 00:37:45,990
Stop here, please.

669
00:37:50,130 --> 00:37:50,750
Thank you.

670
00:37:50,770 --> 00:37:51,700
Thank you, miss.

671
00:38:10,760 --> 00:38:11,490
Hello,

672
00:38:11,510 --> 00:38:12,280
I'd like a pot of tea.

673
00:38:12,280 --> 00:38:12,870
Okay.

674
00:38:29,030 --> 00:38:29,830
Thank you.

675
00:38:29,840 --> 00:38:30,760
Please enjoy.

676
00:38:37,030 --> 00:38:37,890
Let me tell you,

677
00:38:37,890 --> 00:38:39,700
I'm your older brother after all.

678
00:38:39,700 --> 00:38:40,830
Although what you said is right,

679
00:38:40,830 --> 00:38:42,360
you should listen to me too.

680
00:38:42,690 --> 00:38:44,290
At least consider it, right?

681
00:39:15,480 --> 00:39:16,610
Sexual harassment!

682
00:39:16,730 --> 00:39:17,290
Mi Lan.

683
00:39:17,290 --> 00:39:17,960
Help!

684
00:40:06,310 --> 00:40:07,350
It's NBIS's car.

685
00:40:07,930 --> 00:40:08,540
Let's go!

686
00:40:30,690 --> 00:40:31,320
Hongqi.

687
00:40:32,150 --> 00:40:33,130
I told you so.

688
00:40:33,150 --> 00:40:34,520
The NBIS people aren't reliable.

689
00:40:34,520 --> 00:40:35,390
They can't be trusted.

690
00:40:35,390 --> 00:40:36,450
You still believe in them so much

691
00:40:36,450 --> 00:40:38,450
and try to cooperate with them. You—

692
00:40:39,440 --> 00:40:40,220
Miss Mi Lan,

693
00:40:40,290 --> 00:40:41,620
what are you doing here?

694
00:40:41,850 --> 00:40:43,910
Shouldn't you be at work at this time?

695
00:40:44,130 --> 00:40:45,600
I did go to work today,

696
00:40:46,290 --> 00:40:47,980
but then I felt really unwell.

697
00:40:48,540 --> 00:40:51,520
The head nurse told me to come home and rest.

698
00:40:52,220 --> 00:40:53,690
But when I got back to my house,

699
00:40:53,690 --> 00:40:54,990
after getting out of the car,

700
00:40:54,990 --> 00:40:57,080
I noticed something was wrong.

701
00:40:57,410 --> 00:40:58,870
There were a lot of people,

702
00:40:59,280 --> 00:41:01,630
and they seemed to be carrying guns.

703
00:41:03,390 --> 00:41:04,490
There were two groups of people.

704
00:41:04,490 --> 00:41:06,360
The ones shooting at us weren't from the NBIS.

705
00:41:06,360 --> 00:41:07,870
You can even tell that?

706
00:41:08,960 --> 00:41:10,290
You might not have noticed.

707
00:41:10,290 --> 00:41:11,490
When we were running,

708
00:41:11,650 --> 00:41:13,520
Wen Yeming was fighting with those people.

709
00:41:13,520 --> 00:41:15,000
shooting straight for the vital spots.

710
00:41:15,000 --> 00:41:16,120
She was serious.

711
00:41:18,750 --> 00:41:20,680
Then how did they know we were here?

712
00:41:21,690 --> 00:41:23,210
Li's rice noodles.

713
00:41:23,730 --> 00:41:25,330
Delicious rice noodles.

714
00:41:27,360 --> 00:41:28,820
I might have accidentally

715
00:41:28,830 --> 00:41:31,290
given something away during the phone call.

716
00:41:33,230 --> 00:41:34,110
May also be...

717
00:41:36,730 --> 00:41:37,530
What is it?

718
00:41:39,480 --> 00:41:40,850
Myna had his ID with him.

719
00:41:41,020 --> 00:41:42,420
It has his real name on it.

720
00:41:42,830 --> 00:41:45,630
It wouldn't be difficult to trace his background.

721
00:41:54,290 --> 00:41:55,690
Why are you looking at me?

722
00:41:56,540 --> 00:41:57,690
Who is Myna?

723
00:42:00,040 --> 00:42:01,970
Does he have anything to do with me?

724
00:42:04,770 --> 00:42:05,690
Say something.

725
00:42:06,360 --> 00:42:07,970
Why aren't you saying anything?

726
00:42:07,970 --> 00:42:09,300
What exactly happened?

727
00:42:10,450 --> 00:42:11,330
Say something!

728
00:42:12,470 --> 00:42:13,170
Mi Lan,

729
00:42:17,940 --> 00:42:19,470
Myna's real name

730
00:42:20,670 --> 00:42:21,600
is Mi Xingwei.

731
00:42:24,140 --> 00:42:25,070
He was murdered.

732
00:42:30,520 --> 00:42:31,650
That's impossible.

733
00:42:34,540 --> 00:42:35,380
My father...

734
00:42:35,870 --> 00:42:38,530
my father is living well by himself in Shanghai.

735
00:42:38,590 --> 00:42:39,850
He can't be in trouble.

736
00:42:41,810 --> 00:42:42,850
You lied to me.

737
00:42:43,170 --> 00:42:44,500
You lied, didn't you?

738
00:42:47,700 --> 00:42:49,080
This can't be true.

739
00:42:49,800 --> 00:42:51,460
My father can't be in trouble.

740
00:42:52,210 --> 00:42:53,890
He's fine in Shanghai.

741
00:42:54,260 --> 00:42:55,650
How could anything happen to him?

742
00:42:55,650 --> 00:42:56,730
You bad people!

743
00:43:02,050 --> 00:43:02,970
You lied.
